  "description": {
    "zh": "雇佣兵，借一步说话。我接了一个消灭不同阵营PMC的单子，需要是高等级的。让我的小弟们去做，简直就是送死，所以我建议派你去解决问题。你觉得呢？为了证明你的成果，你需要带来两个阵营PMC的狗牌。",
    "en": "Mercenary, come here for a minute. I have an order of elimination of several groups of PMCs, the highly experienced ones. Sending my soldiers to this would be a suicide mission, so that is why I suggest you to handle this matter. What do you say? As proof of the work done, you have to bring me dogtags from both of those groups."
  },
